<div id="pf1" class="pf w0 h0" data-page-no="1"><div class="pc pc1 w0 h0"><img class="bi x0 y0 w1 h1" alt="" src="data:image/png;base64,"/><div class="c x0 y1 w2 h0"><div class="t m0 x1 h2 y2 ff1 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">User Guide </div><div class="t m0 x2 h3 y3 ff2 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">NOTE: The GU<span class="_ _0"></span>I is design<span class="_ _0"></span>ed for the resolutio<span class="_ _0"></span>n: 1920<span class="_ _0"></span>x1200 and may<span class="_ _0"></span> not display<span class="_ _0"></span> properly on </div><div class="t m0 x2 h3 y4 ff2 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">other configuration<span class="_ _0"></span>s. </div><div class="t m0 x2 h4 y5 ff1 fs2 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Screen 1 </div><div class="t m0 x3 h5 y6 ff3 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">This screen allow<span class="_ _0"></span>s the user to con<span class="_ _0"></span>figure the dim<span class="_ _0"></span>ensions of the d<span class="_ _0"></span>rone cag<span class="_ _0"></span>e being used. <span class="_ _0"></span>The </div><div class="t m0 x2 h5 y7 ff3 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">dropdown menu con<span class="_ _0"></span>tains s<span class="_ _0"></span>aved cage configuration<span class="_ _0"></span>s as well as <span class="_ _0"></span>the option to con<span class="_ _0"></span>figure a <span class="_ _0"></span>new cage. Saved </div><div class="t m0 x2 h5 y8 ff3 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">cage configurat<span class="_ _0"></span>ions are edit lock<span class="_ _0"></span>ed by defaul<span class="_ _0"></span>t, but can be ed<span class="_ _0"></span>ited after c<span class="_ _0"></span>licking on t<span class="_ _0"></span>he edit togg<span class="_ _0"></span>le. Click </div><div class="t m0 x2 h5 y9 ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">“Select” when ready<span class="_ _0"></span> to proceed w<span class="_ _0"></span>ith the curren<span class="_ _0"></span>tly selected <span class="_ _0"></span>cage configura<span class="_ _0"></span>tion<span class="ff3"> </span></div><div class="t m0 x2 h4 ya ff1 fs2 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Screen 2 </div><div class="t m0 x3 h5 yb ff3 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">This screen allow<span class="_ _0"></span>s the user to con<span class="_ _0"></span>figure the sen<span class="_ _0"></span>sors being<span class="_ _0"></span> used. The upperm<span class="_ _0"></span>ost dropdown m<span class="_ _0"></span>enu </div><div class="t m0 x2 h5 yc ff3 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">allows the select<span class="_ _0"></span>ion of exist<span class="_ _0"></span>ing sensors <span class="_ _0"></span>for modificat<span class="_ _0"></span>ion or the sel<span class="_ _0"></span>ection of a new <span class="_ _0"></span>sensor. As s<span class="_ _0"></span>ensor </div><div class="t m0 x2 h5 yd ff3 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">configuration dat<span class="_ _0"></span>a is m<span class="_ _0"></span>odified, the user can s<span class="_ _0"></span>ee a visual representat<span class="_ _0"></span>ion of the senso<span class="_ _0"></span>r as well. Sens<span class="_ _0"></span>or data </div><div class="t m0 x2 h6 ye ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">is not saved unt<span class="_ _0"></span>il the “Save” button <span class="_ _0"></span>is clicked.
